            },
            {
              "text": "value, some Unicode scalars are represented in UTF-16 by a pair of",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "16-bit code units. The first and second code units of the pair,",
              "type": "text"
